    <question>
        <prompt>What role did Bernard Baruch play during World War I?</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">He was a military general</option>
            <option letter="b">He led the War Industries Board</option>
            <option letter="c">He was a peace negotiator</option>
            <option letter="d">He commanded the navy</option>
        </options>
        <answer>b</answer>
        <explanation>Bernard Baruch headed the War Industries Board, coordinating and directing America's industrial production efforts during World War I to support the war effort.</explanation>
